  "text": "Although bone tunnel enlargement does not appear to influence primary graft stability [CITATION_1] , in case of revision it may make the procedure more difficult to perform, as two-stage revision surgery with bone grafting and delayed ligament reconstruction may be necessary [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] .",
